name: sunrose
description:
If only my death was written today.
Don't cry for me,
Cause I'm the happy one,
Because the heart is being possessed by your love.
If the time comes,
Happiness you will see clearly,
In my mouth full of smiles.

Rose ,
I have made you my last flower.
Which became the fragrance on my bed.
Let me sleep peacefully with your love, in a long rest.
